## Title: ShardTrim
## Notes: Deletes one excess Soul Shard per `/shardtrim` or `/st` use, trimming down toward a configurable keep count. Supports `/shardtrim <number>` to set the keep amount, `/shardtrim reset` to restore the default, and `/shardtrim help` for usage details.
